                  PrintableLiteMessage.class,
                  "getLabel",
                  new Class<?>[0]
          );
          Object value = invokeOrDie.invokeWithArguments(
                  accessor,
                  new PrintableLiteMessage(),
                  new Object[0]
          );
  
          assertThat(value).isEqualTo(LABEL);
